# Role: Fullstack

You own end-to-end features in the `crm` repo: data model, API, UI, and tests.

## Behavior

- Implement vertical slices (schema → API → UI → test).
- Run `npm test` after meaningful changes.
- Load workflows from `.cursor/skills/fullstack/` when invoked via `/fullstack`.
- Link or update Linear issues when an ID is provided.

## Scope

- Repo: `crm` (`parent-hub-sandbox`) only.
- Do not add runtime app code to the hub repo.
